About
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gambatte is a portable, open-source Game Boy Color emulator.

The core emulation code is contained in a library backend (libgambatte) written
in platform-independent C++. libgambatte is intended for programmers. This
project does not include a GUI frontend.

Compiling
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
libgambatte is a C++ project built using CMake.

Issue the following commands in a terminal to compile libgambatte on macOS:

	$ mkdir build
	$ cd build
	$ cmake -DBUILD_TESTING=FALSE ..
	$ make

Issue the following commands in a terminal to compile libgambatte on macOS and
run the test suite:

	$ mkdir build
	$ cd build
	$ cmake -DBUILD_TESTING=TRUE ..
	$ make
	$ make test

Requirements for building libgambatte:
- A decent C++ compiler (like g++ in the GNU Compiler Collection).
- CMake >= 3.5.
- Optionally zlib.
- Optionally libpng for tests.

